author: arkurth
msg: Added VIM_SSH.pm::_check_service_pid. This checks if the contents of a service's PID file matches the parent service process. If they do not match, the PID file is updated. This is done before 'services.sh restart' is called.
Added a semaphore to the _services_restart subroutine so that multiple processes for the same VM host do not attempt to restart the services at the same time.
